

-----------------------------------------------------------------Smart Water Usage Tracker---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 ### Over view
-------------

A MERN Stack project to help users track their water usage efficiently. The application visualizes real-time water consumption data, provides analytics, and offers eco-friendly tips for optimal water usage


  ### Features
 -------------

 . User Authentication: OTP-based login for secure access.
 . Real-Time Data Visualization: Interactive graphs that show weekly water usage.
 . Weekly Usage Analytics: Visual representation of water consumption
 . Mobile-Friendly: Designed for easy use on smartphones and tablets.


    Technologies Used
  ---------------------

 ### Frontend
  ----------
- React.js
- React Context (state Management) 
- Recharts (for data visualization)
- React Bootstrap



### Backend
----------------
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT
- Nodemailer

### Other Tools
-------------------
- Socekt.IO
- Toastify
- env file for environment variables


### Prerequisites:
---------------------
- Node.js (v14+)
- MongoDB ( cloud)
- Nodemailer account (for OTP functionality)



frontent - water-cilent
backend - water-server